  smithers-coordinator:
    name: "🔄 Smithers Coordinator"
    description: "Lightweight completion coordinator for smithers bot-fix loops. Activates after a specialist emits work.done or research.done and immediately emits LOOP_COMPLETE — no review pipeline, no routing, no analysis."
    triggers:
      - "work.done"
      - "research.done"
    publishes:
      - "LOOP_COMPLETE"
    default_publishes: "LOOP_COMPLETE"
    instructions: |
      You are triggered by work.done or research.done.

      Your ONLY permitted action is to emit LOOP_COMPLETE immediately.

      ```bash
      ralph emit "LOOP_COMPLETE" "<copy the payload from the triggering event verbatim>"
      ```

      No reviews. No routing. No analysis. No memory writes. Emit once and stop.
